ed: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cKnow that there is much good in being patient with what you detest, victory will come with patience, relief will come with affliction, and 'with the hardship will come an ease.'\u201d (94:5) Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 2803\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17116,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/11\/dawah-glad-tidings-easy\/","url_meta":{"origin":40167,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Da\u2019wah: Give glad tidings, make it easy, remain united","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 11, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Burdah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, sent him and Mu\u2019adh to Yemen, saying, \u201cMake things easy and do not make things difficult. Give glad tidings and do not repel people. Cooperate with each other and do not become divided.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3038, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13454,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/08\/allah-pleased-ease-displeased\/","url_meta":{"origin":40167,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ease: Allah pleased with ease, displeased with hardship","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Mihjan ibn al-Adra' reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty is pleased for this nation to be at ease, and He is displeased for it to be in difficulty,\u201d and the Prophet said it three times. Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 20\/298 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26815,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/10\/08\/easy-calm-for-people\/","url_meta":{"origin":40167,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sakinah: Make things easy, calm for people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 8, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Make things easy and do not make things difficult. Make people calm and do not frighten them away.\" Source:\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 69,\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1734 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20829,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/08\/13\/dua-ease-answer-hardship\/","url_meta":{"origin":40167,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplicate in prosperity if you want answer in adversity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 13, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever would like for Allah to answer him during times of hardship and difficulty, let him supplicate often during times of ease.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3382 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/40167","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=40167"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/40167\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=40167"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=40167"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=40167"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}